              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The intensities of the spectra were converted to",
                "absolute cross sections through the use of a monitor",
                "detector of known solid angle in the target chamber to",
                "record  elastically scattered beam particles at",
                " 42-degree.The elastic scattering cross section was",
                "not measured, but was taken from a DWBA calculation to",
                "be 014 b/sr for 40 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were prepared from oxide material enriched",
                "to 95.5% in Sm-150.The oxide was reduced to metal and",
                "the metal evaporated onto a 27 mug/cm**2 carbon foil.",
                "The target thickness was about 180 mug/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*EN-RSL-FW*.The average energy resolution was typically",
                " 25 keV(FWHM)"
              ]
            }
          ],
